{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9781,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「念のため、火爆破しときましょうか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Just to be safe, shall we do a fire explosion?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9782,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ア、ッ………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, ugh............\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9783,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アホかーーーーーーーーーーーー！！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Are you an idiotーーーーーーーーーーーー!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9784,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アニスはぽーいと放り捨てられた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anise was casually thrown aside."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9785,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれあれ？　もしもーし。開けてくださーい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh? Helloo~. Please open up~\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9786,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やかましい！　魔力が空っぽになってから",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Noisy! Come back after your magic power is completely empty"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9787,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　出直してこい！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and start over!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9788,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アニスがやってきた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anise arrived."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9789,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いいわね、言われた通りのものを買って、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, buy exactly what you were told,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9790,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　戻ってくるのよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and come back.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9791,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい！　お買い物ですね！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes! Shopping it is!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9792,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お任せください！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Leave it to me!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9793,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それと、魔法は……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And also, about the magic...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9794,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「では！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9795,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あっ…………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9796,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アニスは千鶴子の話を最後まで聞くことなく、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anise didn't listen to Chizuruko's story until the end,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9797,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そのまま飛び出していった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and immediately dashed out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9798,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「毎度の、事だけど……心配だわ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's the usual thing, but... I'm worried...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9799,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔法さえなければ、大丈夫なのですが……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If only it weren't for the magic, it would be fine, but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9800,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔法を禁止するとか……無理ですよね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Banning magic... that's impossible, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9801,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あの子の場合、放出できないと体調崩すの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"In that child's case, if she can't release it, her physical condition worsens."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9802,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　体内で勝手に生まれる魔力が強すぎる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " The magic power that spontaneously forms inside her body is too strong.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9803,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「じゃ、どうにか放出量を絞るしかないですね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Then, there's no choice but to somehow reduce the amount released...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9804,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「とっくにやってるわよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We've already done that long ago."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9805,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あの杖は広域魔法の範囲を絞る杖だし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " That staff narrows the area of wide-range magic,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9806,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　額冠は集中を高める魔法を使い続ける物だし……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and the forehead crown continues to use magic that increases concentration...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9807,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あの子の全身のその手の装備、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That child's all those kinds of equipment on her entire body,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9808,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ほとんど魔法犯罪者の抑止用の代物よ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " are mostly things to restrain magical criminals.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9809,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「同じ物つけて動けるのは……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The only one who can move wearing the same things..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9810,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ガンジー王くらいじゃないかしら」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " is probably King Gandhi.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9811,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う、うわぁ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"U-uwah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9812,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「じゃああの髪留めも？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Then, what about that hairpin?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9813,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あれは……………別に。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is... nothing special."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9814,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まあ、似合うかな、と…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Well, it kind of suits her...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9815,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「可愛がってはいるんだ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I do care for her...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9816,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん…………まあ。でも…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... well, but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9817,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あいつ、そういうの全部裏切るのよーーーー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That girl betrays all of thatーーーー!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9818,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もーーーーーーーーーーー！！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Daaaaaaaaaaamn it!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9819,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは…………まぁ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, that's... yeah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9820,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーんふーん、るーららー。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm hmm, ru-rara~."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9821,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お買い物ったらお買い物ー♪」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Shopping means shopping~♪\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9822,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「千鶴子様の、てろてろラーメン♪",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Chizuruko-sama's, silky ramen♪"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9823,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　楽しみですー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I'm looking forward to it~\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9824,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ひっ、アニス様！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eek, Anise-sama!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9825,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アニス様よ！　逃げろ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Anise-sama! Run away!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9826,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ヘソをとられるぞー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"They're going to take your belly button!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9827,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アニス様注意報は現在出ていません！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"There is currently no warning for Anise-sama!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9828,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　落ち着いて行動してください！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Please act calmly!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9829,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　繰り返します、注意報はまだ出ていません！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I repeat, no warning has been issued yet!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9830,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はー。今日も街は賑やかですねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Haa. The town is lively today as well~\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9831,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さてそろそろ…………はっ！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, soon... huh!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9832,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "アニスは目的の店の前で、足を止めた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anise stopped in front of the shop she was aiming for."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9833,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お、お店が閉まっています……潰れた？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"T-the shop is closed... Has it gone out of business?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9834,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はっ、もしや魔物の仕業！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha! Could this be the work of monsters!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9835,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この辺りに魔物の進攻が！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Monsters are invading this area!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9836,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "構えた杖の先に、目視できるほどの魔力が集まる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Magic power visible to the eye gathered at the tip of the raised staff."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9837,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ひっ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eek!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9838,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………見当たりませんし止めましょう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...There is none in sight, so let's stop this."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9839,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それより食材を探さなくては」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " More importantly, we have to find ingredients.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9840,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "収束した魔力が霧散する。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The concentrated magic power dispersed into mist."
    }
  ]
}

